      <title>贷款需求旺盛，印度银行短期债务升至 12 年来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/indian-banks-short-term-debt-rise-to-12-year-high-on-loan-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度银行越来越多地转向短期借贷来弥补因贷款强劲增长和存款减少而导致的资金短缺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/indian-banks-short-term-debt-rise-to-12-year-high-on-loan-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
