    <item>
      <title>暗黑舰队行动暴露了拥挤的马六甲海峡周边的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/dark-fleet-oil-tanker-s-caper-exposes-growing-risks-in-crowded-malacca-strait</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡附近海域两艘油轮相撞并起火，凸显出马六甲海峡周边风险的日益增加，因为暗海船队规模不断扩大，而中国需求低迷导致数十艘油轮处于闲置状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/dark-fleet-oil-tanker-s-caper-exposes-growing-risks-in-crowded-malacca-strait</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 09:19:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
