      <title>金能集团为煤矿签署 6 亿美元私人贷款协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/golden-energy-group-inks-600-million-private-loan-for-coal-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，由 Golden Energy and Resources Pte Ltd. 牵头的财团已与 Davidson Kempner Capital Management LP 等私人信贷基金签署了一项 6 亿美元贷款协议，用于支付其收购澳大利亚煤矿的费用。]]></description>
